/ph><props><value key="prefix"></value><value key="localName">ph</value><value key="namespaces"></value><value key="isEmptyElement">False</value><value key="nodeType">Element</value><value key="displayText">&lt;uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " id="uicontrol68001436163214" conref="en-us_topic_0000207784739017.xml#490618" idp:usecustomid="x-wc://file=ZH-CN_TOPIC_0000207784739017.xml#490618" idp:conrefpath="200650494000#EN-US_BOOKMAP_0000002298267098#EN-US_TOPIC_0000207784739017"/&gt;</value><value key="hasDisplayText">True</value><value key="attribute:id">f1</value></props></tag></tag-defs></header><body><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="0e205526-2a09-42df-a7a8-15159482a673"><source>Why Is No Electricity Being Sold from the Battery?</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Why Is No Electricity Being Sold from the Battery?</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Waarom wordt er geen elektriciteit verkocht vanuit de batterij?</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="1"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">Rqv6FdUIzabikFjJk752JwjJffY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="450ce1ae-7ccf-4811-a657-3254e8b362c9"><source>Function constraints</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Function constraints</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Functiebeperkingen</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="2"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">tsXZQ8iDe/TnJNzcSzdoXzwm+yQ=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="96687c42-8256-4112-b6fb-ea0f496a7f22"><source>The <x id="0" /> function may not have been enabled.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">The <x id="0" /> function may not have been enabled.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">De functie <x id="0" /> is mogelijk niet ingeschakeld.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="3"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">be9/TALGeDLZ+lfnuw7PTOyFirw=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="02129c17-3996-4e1f-8bb7-c72df0446de4"><source>If this function is disabled, the system will not discharge to the grid even if the conditions for selling electricity are met.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">If this function is disabled, the system will not discharge to the grid even if the conditions for selling electricity are met.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Als deze functie is uitgeschakeld, zal het systeem niet naar het net ontladen, zelfs niet als aan de voorwaarden voor de verkoop van elektriciteit wordt voldaan.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="4"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">7VoJPiyQ8c9Hv9zhkAQDHpBJj5A=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="035eae09-0357-4ecf-9a75-23eead09b672"><source>Economic considerations</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Economic considerations</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Economische overwegingen</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="5"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">14k0lADpxHLkDVwcYPVjpTvZuHU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="1c85938b-e49d-43cf-bc2a-9951e83fc330"><source>The battery performs intelligent scheduling based on economic considerations:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">The battery performs intelligent scheduling based on economic considerations:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">De batterij voert intelligente planning uit op basis van economische overwegingen:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">8e+G1Q8mOmPHe9t14AyVLVBD590=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="ec85a939-4367-4792-9c2a-d3efeae23b01"><source><g id="3">Price difference</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7"><g id="3">Price difference</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7"><g id="3">Prijsverschil</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">IPfO6MyhbOs+xVYdAbE6Rp9jTzM=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="8b2850d6-6fca-44db-8dd3-2614d04b565c"><source>If the difference between the current feed-in price and the purchase price is small, the returns from battery discharge are limited.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">If the difference between the current feed-in price and the purchase price is small, the returns from battery discharge are limited.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">Als het verschil tussen de huidige terugleveringsprijs en de inkoopprijs klein is, zijn de opbrengsten van het ontladen van de batterij beperkt.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="8"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">rSxEImhww0iL8j7klARkl7m5c7k=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="06fc1bf4-d1d7-46dc-8e47-d4c80e87360e"><source>The system may reserve energy and discharge it during higher electricity price periods the next day to obtain greater returns.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">The system may reserve energy and discharge it during higher electricity price periods the next day to obtain greater returns.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">Het systeem kan energie reserveren en deze de volgende dag ontladen tijdens periodes met hogere elektriciteitsprijzen om hogere opbrengsten te behalen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="9"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">LoQdvHZYxMyZ9U7k6XQNF9g6Ses=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="bad7413e-530b-49ae-92ba-4fdb89ae4f64"><source><g id="6">Returns maximization policy</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10"><g id="6">Returns maximization policy</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10"><g id="6">Beleid voor maximalisatie van opbrengsten</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="10"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">GRKUIa1kNfeoJez8ue9dH8FwSfY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="8bba70c5-43e8-4979-a391-8af3afb9af72"><source>The system forecasts electricity price fluctuations and prioritizes discharging during peak electricity price periods.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">The system forecasts electricity price fluctuations and prioritizes discharging during peak electricity price periods.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">Het systeem voorspelt schommelingen in de elektriciteitsprijs en geeft prioriteit aan ontladen tijdens piekperiodes van elektriciteitsprijzen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="11"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">py7PDC/KX9XP+uUnuC41/e72JWk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="687a02d9-e0a8-43e1-aee7-98f23d421019"><source>If the current electricity price is not high, the battery may remain in standby mode.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">If the current electricity price is not high, the battery may remain in standby mode.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">Als de huidige elektriciteitsprijs niet hoog is, kan de batterij in stand-bymodus blijven.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="12"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">QQpQoQmRroC2uotMsSZHhaF5w5s=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="15c54e69-780a-4d47-bf1e-5e1a4da9b9d8"><source>SOC protection</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">SOC protection</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">SOC-beveiliging</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="13"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">seRrr9YJZCuSEJhe+eovTxHzfKI=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="c1e3e56b-7fae-44ce-a401-2da239d312bb"><source>If the battery SOC falls below the end-of-discharge threshold (for example, <x id="7" /> or <x id="8" />), the system stops discharging to ensure power supply capacity during unexpected outages.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">If the battery SOC falls below the end-of-discharge threshold (for example, <x id="7" /> or <x id="8" />), the system stops discharging to ensure power supply capacity during unexpected outages.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">Als de SOC van de batterij onder de ontlaaddrempel valt (bijvoorbeeld <x id="7" /> of <x id="8" />), stopt het systeem met ontladen om de stroomvoorziening te waarborgen bij onverwachte storingen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="14"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">nWFDuQSwGPhbamTJLJ3Thq6/xFo=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group></body></file></xliff>